      "author_association" : "CONTRIBUTOR",
      "body" : "> So in the end the parameter would need to be distributed the same way as `signetchallenge`\r\n\r\nI had similar thoughts and think eventually we may want to introduce a more encompassing (and upgradeable) parameter such as `-signetconfig` in which all signet consensus parameters are encoded (currently just challenge and blocktime), but I think starting with the current modular approach is fine given that it's signet.",
